Text: RENeal At this time you do not have a profile on CERAcom Following are instructions for establishing one Create your profile on ceracom Open your web browser and go to clientnewaccount The first screen you will enter will ask for your COMPANY USERNAME and PASSWORD The Enron Corp username is enron The Enron Corp password is ravencall As you begin to initiate the account creation process you must create your OWN username and password Please DO NOT use the Enron Corp username and password After entering your contact details you will be asked to customize a profile that allows you to receive email notification of specific pieces of research that interest you To look up reports on the CERA web site go to click on log in to client services enter your OWN USERNAME and PASSWORD and select the corresponding CERA knowledge area such as European Gas or use the search function When you receive email notification of new content on the CERA web site follow the hyperlink URL to the actual report on the CERA web site To access the new report you will be asked to enter your OWN USERNAME and PASSWORD If you have any questions about ceracom please do not hesitate to contact me Stephen Burke Cambridge Energy Research Associates Original Message From mailto Sent Wednesday April PM To Subject I have forgotten my user name and password I work for Enron Can you help me Thank you Scott Neal
